### Upload resume
# Select the `local` environment in the REST Client extension and update
# `resumeFile`, `resumeFileName`, and `resumeContentType` in `rest-client.env.json`.
# @name uploadResume
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ATSRefinerUploadBoundary

------ATSRefinerUploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="{{resumeFileName}}"
Content-Type: {{resumeContentType}}

< {{resumeFile}}
------ATSRefinerUploadBoundary--
